    <item>
      <title>Phd Commits</title>
      <link>lazappi.id.au/project/phd-commits/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2019 17:45:06 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>lazappi.id.au/project/phd-commits/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;R scripts that can be used to scrape the git commit history of a project. The
commits can then be categorised and used to produce a animated plot of the
project over time as shown below. This was originally created as a way of
displaying activity of my PhD but could be used for any project.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lazappi/phd-commits/master/phd_commits.gif&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
